<h3><em>Workshop:</em> Scalable and Modular Architecture for CSS</h3>
<p>This workshop will shift how you think about writing CSS. It will simplify your code, making your project easier to manage, and allowing it to grow without creating an increasingly brittle system of dependencies. Your code will also be more portable, making it easier to use components in various contexts and in other projects.</p>
