<h3>Becoming a Deep Generalist</h3>
<p>A jack of all trades and master of none. We’re told that we can either go deep on a particular topic or go general. After all, how can someone actually know everything about everything? However, with the right focus and plenty of time, we can become magical unicorns of design and development.</p>

