<h3>How to Write a Book</h3>
<p>For many people, as it was for me, writing a book is a feather in their cap. It’s a moment of pride to hold your work in your hands. How to Write a Book looks at the hurdles—technical and otherwise—in writing a tech book including how and why you might self-publish. By the end of the session, maybe you’ll be inspired to write your own book.</p>

